{"tid":1297624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"if you can’t beat them, join them","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:31.000Z","uid":172093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5823c1b173f0b19ece6a25960d5478409de30d","tid":1297624,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"連登作為其中一個藍絲集中地<br />\n係時候都要搞d活動去撐警<br />\n我希望大家可以去警總支持警察<br />\n等警察明白我地連登係真藍絲<br />\n我地提出有四大訴求<br />\n一. 支持警察全面取締立法 司法制度<br />\n二. 成立香港警賊政府 警黑合作 統治香港<br />\n三. 設立特權制度 萬般皆下品 唯有警察高<br />\n四. 林奠已死 一哥當立 支持盧偉聰成為新一代特首<br />\n<br />\n為左阻止黃屍繼續禍港 係時候要出黎做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 死黑警 明撐你呀宜家</span></span>"},{"pid":"3dbc7b4ce5720c021bd54a639acd88810491b6c9","tid":1297624,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"888897ce250205589541ffbb5e9bbc35ce5e0f27","tid":1297624,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a79929185ff2c7ea15ee07fdfc9cd953601391","tid":1297624,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}